Lacey Spears of Kentucky was spared the maximum 25 years to life in the death of her son Garnett-Paul Spears . 
  The boy's father Chris Hill lashed out at his ex on Facebook this week . 
  Spears was found guilty last month of second-degree murder for poisoning her son with salt at a New York hospital . 
  She appeared emotionless as she was sentenced and showed no emotion at her sentencing on Wednesday . 
  The judge said the crime was 'unfathomable in its cruelty'